0.03 2024-04-24
    * More caching of Twitch data
    * Allow downloading multiple Twitch streams in one invocation of scripts/twitch-record-live.pl
    * Added a --dry-run option
    * Now uses asynchronous HTTP integrating with other event loops

0.02 2023-07-21
    * Support other output filename formats in duplicate detection
    * Better stale recording detection
    * More caching to hit the network less often
    * By default, record lower resolution video
    * Fix prerequisites in META.*
    * Various test suite updates

0.01 2022-03-08
    * Released on an unsuspecting world
